summary.span: 提供返回预定义 实例的静态属性，这些实例对应于 Unicode 规范中的块。

span.span: Provides static properties that return predefined instances that correspond to blocks from the Unicode specification.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 您可以使用 属性来检索名为的 unicode 区域，其中每个都包含一个连续的 unicode 码位块。You use properties to retrieve Unicode named ranges, each of which consists of a contiguous block of Unicode code points. 某些范围包含未定义的码位。Some ranges include undefined code points. 例如，在 **亚美尼亚语** Unicode 块 (u +0530 + 058F) 、u + 0530、u +0557 + 0558、u + 0560、u + 0588 和 u + 058B-058C 未定义。For example, in the **Armenian** Unicode block (U+0530-U+058F), U+0530, U+0557-U+0558, U+0560, U+0588, and U+058B-058C are undefined. 一个或多个未定义的码位可以出现在某个范围的开头、某个范围的末尾或两者之间的任何位置。One or more undefined code points can occur at the beginning of a range, at the end of a range, or anywhere in between. 目前， 该类仅支持基本多语言平面中的命名范围 (BMP) ，后者从 u + 0000 到 u + FFFF。Currently, the class supports only named ranges in the Basic Multilingual Plane (BMP), which extends from U+0000 to U+FFFF.
